name: peak matching
description: Peak matching is a data transformation performed on a dataset of a graph of ordered data points (e.g. a spectrum) with the objective of pattern matching local maxima above a noise threshold

name: mass spectrometry analysis
description: A data transformation which has the objective of spectrum analysis.

name: gas chromatography mass spectrometry
description: Gas chromatography mass spectrometry is a data transformation combining mass spectrometry and   gas chromatography for the qualitative as well as quantitative   determinations of compounds.
